{"word":"ἄπαγε","slug":"ἄπαγε","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἄπαγε</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>properly the imperat of <a href='S:ἀπάγω'><el>ἀπάγω</el></a>, in <a href='S:intransitive'>intr.</a> sense.\n<p/><i>away! begone! hands off!</i> <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>apage!</el> <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/>"}]}